<text>
<body>
<div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_000941_0001" n="0001"/>

<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName>Mission House
<lb/>Blomfield <choice><abbr>St</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice>
<lb/>London</placeName> <date when="1856-01-06">6<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi>
	<choice><abbr>Jan</abbr><expan>January</expan></choice>
<lb/>1856</date></dateline>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>

<lb/><p>The time which
<lb/>I can spend in <country>England</country>
<lb/>is so very sort
<lb/>I am obliged to decline
<lb/>all invitations of
<lb/>the kind you mention
<lb/>and even were it
<lb/>otherwise I am unfitted

	<pb facs="liv_000941_0002" n="0002"/>

<lb/>for lecturing in
<lb/>English by long
<lb/>disuse of that tongue
<lb/>and a firm convention
<lb/>that my sphere of
<lb/>usefulness does not
<lb/>lie in public <unclear cert="high">exhibitions</unclear>
<lb/>at all. I hope then
<lb/>you will <unclear cert="medium">humbly</unclear>
<lb/>make my excuse
<lb/>to the young men's

	<pb facs="liv_000941_0003" n="0003"/>

<lb/><term type="faith">christian</term> association
<lb/>some of them may
<lb/>yet be missionaries
<lb/>themselves and
<lb/>may be able to
<lb/>supply at some future
<lb/>time my lack of
<lb/>service so the <gap extent="1" unit="words"/><!-- I'm not sure what to gleam here. Not sure if covered by tape. Could be "D 5", but I don't know what that could refer to. BL-->
<lb/>need not be
<lb/><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="blot"/><!-- Could possibly be "book", but I'm not confident in that choice. BL--> <unclear cert="low">thesuple</unclear><!-- legible text, I just can't figure out what word. BL-->
<lb/>cannot come, yet
<lb/>I <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> say "<unclear cert="low">I pree</unclear> it."

	<pb facs="liv_000941_0004" n="0004"/>

<lb/>wishing the association
<lb/>much success &amp;
<lb/>thanking you most
<lb/>heartily for your
<lb/>kind offers of
<lb/>hospitality I am</p>

<lb/><closer><salute><space extent="1" unit="chars"></space>Dear Sir Most
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"></space>Sincerely yours</salute>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="chars"></space><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer>


            </div>
